ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"屌回錯po sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c17ea959709a938041dec53160a84eb93752c0cb","tid":1917040,"uid":157872,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"The idiom originates from ancient and medieval societies of Europe and distinguishes an upper class (whose superficial veins appeared blue through their <span style=\"color: red;\">untanned skin</span>) from a working class of the time. The latter consisted mainly of agricultural peasants who spent most of their time working outdoors and thus had tanned skin, through which superficial veins appear less prominently."}]}